{"tid":482680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住九龍城，覺得沙中線唔係特別方便","createTime":"2017-11-28T11:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T12:17:41.000Z","uid":137038,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"af68c2508769a05c0c44a6348c626b2a917dccb1","tid":482680,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"最近係網上同電視見有不少沙中線廣告，但我諗諗下覺得其實唔會帶來好大方便<br />\n<br />\n東西走廊係九龍嘅走線係由鑽石山經啟德、土瓜灣去紅磡再接返西鐵，而西鐵站少又遠離中心區域，要去旺區就要轉返地鐵<br />\n<br />\n打開張未來港鐵路線圖睇睇，由宋皇臺出發，不論去旺角/深水埗/佐敦/觀塘，因走線問題，都係要兜路，本來已經有巴士/小巴舒舒服服直到，做乜要罰企+轉車<br />\n<br />\n當過海段通埋車，去銅鑼灣至港島東要轉兩次車，去南區又係要轉兩次車<br />\n<br />\n無疑，去新界係方便咗，彌補咗無直車去荃灣/元朗/北區，但九龍人又有幾可入新界呢"},{"pid":"a51f9989470f37ca3a1b48f9079cda4f2ae66c84","tid":482680,"uid":46042,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"傻左？"},{"pid":"f84a0e9f5621d8a7b40a7aca05e7741a6c5bf69e","tid":482680,"uid":102096,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5db51c1749a95f2d21405daf69236197febaef7","tid":482680,"uid":68711,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"過海轉1次線就話唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾多地方港島以外既地方可以唔駛轉線？"},{"pid":"c8f60e13ee4e13ad972a3de1a6a9a09e69a99b26","tid":482680,"uid":25221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:36:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43cf29c77d2485b87adfb24432263fc0b9bb7773","tid":482680,"uid":48334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"腦裝左屎呀"},{"pid":"dc47623f0e6bb89c4f39ccbb0299c26f79d06606","tid":482680,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"我地住市區邊會諗呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新界咪覺得方便左 對我地黎講唔算好大作用<br />\n佢起條中九龍線經大角咀果啲反而有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2638112280afadfa453a176f4af23a5c1b6a34c","tid":482680,"uid":38537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"1. 沙中線最重要係開多一條市區打直嘅線，由新界經九龍再過海，抒緩九龍塘站嘅擠擁<br />\n2. 短線你可以繼續搭巴士小巴，但經何文田站轉返去太子旺角浪費你幾多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 有邊條線過海去港島東唔洗再轉線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c555c8208f9c1527bf30f08352285c08d1d99e60","tid":482680,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"e8784da079df74adffd7e37d4ef99c33e41be5f6","tid":482680,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"中學生作文噉"},{"pid":"ac46a18fe7eccfce401439a08a3c2876d0619d16","tid":482680,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"中學生作文噉"},{"pid":"2b4cbabde4869204c7cde828714753dcc838df73","tid":482680,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"住紅磡 覺得沙中線唔係特別方便"},{"pid":"225e873dc83b87e5a666697611847746575cb991","tid":482680,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"起到去你屋企門口好無<br />\n屌你老母"}]}